MY H'aMYN LShM'yThNV VZUrV'y YHVH 'yL-MY NGLThH.
VY'yL KYVNQ LPhNYV VKShUrSh M'aUrTSh TShYH L'a-Th'aUr LV VL'a HDUr VNUr'aHV VL'a- MUr'aH VNChMDHV.
NBZH VChDL 'aYShYM 'aYSh MK'aBVTh VYDV'y ChLY VKMSThUr PhNYM MMNV NBZH VL'a ChShBNHV.
'aKN ChLYNV HV'a NSh'a VMK'aBYNV SBLM V'aNChNV ChShBNHV NGV'y MKH 'aLHYM VM'yNH.
VHV'a MChLL MPhSh'yNV MDK'a M'yVNThYNV MVSUr ShLVMNV 'yLYV VBChBUrThV NUrPh'a- LNV.
KLNV KTSh'aN Th'yYNV 'aYSh LDUrKV PhNYNV VYHVH HPhGY'y BV 'aTh 'yVN KLNV.
NGSh VHV'a N'yNH VL'a YPhThCh-PhYV KShH LTBCh YVBL VKUrChL LPhNY GZZYH N'aLMH VL'a YPhThCh PhYV.
M'yTShUr VMMShPhT LQCh V'aTh-DVUrV MY YShVChCh KY NGZUr M'aUrTSh ChYYM MPhSh'y 'yMY NG'y LMV.
VYThN 'aTh-UrSh'yYM QBUrV V'aTh-'yShYUr BMThYV 'yL L'a-ChMS 'yShH VL'a MUrMH BPhYV.
VYHVH ChPhTSh DK'aV HChLY 'aM-ThShYM 'aShM NPhShV YUr'aH ZUr'y Y'aUrYK YMYM VChPhTSh YHVH BYDV YTShLCh.
M'yML NPhShV YUr'aH YShB'y BD'yThV YTShDYQ TShDYQ 'yBDY LUrBYM V'yVNThM HV'a YSBL.
LKN 'aChLQ-LV BUrBYM V'aTh-'yTShVMYM YChLQ ShLL ThChTh 'aShUr H'yUrH LMVTh NPhShV V'aTh-PhSh'yYM NMNH VHV'a ChT'a-UrBYM NSh'a VLPhSh'yYM YPhGY'y.
